title: BRIEF-Sygnity's offer chosen in tender by Bank Gospodarstwa Krajowego
text:
Oct 14 Sygnity SA :
* Said on Tuesday that its 54.0 million zloty ($14.5 million)gross offer was chosen by Bank Gospodarstwa Krajowego as preferable one in tender for delivery of central banking system
